snippet.title: Executive Assault explosive Steam trailer
snippet.description:
A new fresh and action packed trailer is now out for Executive Assault, the Real time Strategy game where you can take control in first person of any robot, tank or mech you have built and lead your army into battle! http://store.steampowered.com/app/331500
Music by international award nominated composer Chris Hesketh 
http://www.heskethmedia.com
